snippet.title: EarthBound Mod Menu - MOTHER Direct 2024 Release Trailer
snippet.description:
DOWNLOAD: https://shrinefox.com/earthbound
MUSIC: virt - Get on the Bus

EARTHBOUND MOD MENU -- Replay EarthBound your way!
This mod collects several quality of life enhancements, some made by myself,
some made by the PK Hack community.

It's open source, so anyone can use parts of it for their own mods,
or create their own derivatives.

THANK YOU TO: Mr. Tenda, Mr. Accident, JTolmar, phoenixbound, Catador, ShadowOne333, vince94, Chaz, cooprocks123e & H.S. for making this mod possible!
